setlist.info: "Loving Cup" makes an extremely rare appearance on the set list for the first time since Atlantic City, 17 Nov 2006. This is only it's 22nd live performance ever dating back to 1969 when it debuted at the free concert in London's Hyde Park. Completely dormant from 1973 to 2001, it was resurrected and played just a handful of times on the Licks and A Bigger Bang tours.
